data.description: This solid 1.5 story home has 3 BR's and 1.75 BA's.  It may be located on a busy street but it has a nice long driveway that provides for at least 4 off street parking spots.  Wonderful covered front porch, lots of original woodwork and wood floors, patio area & partially fenced backyard.  Kitchen has newer appliances that will be staying plus a clothes washer & dryer.  There is also a nice 1.5 detached garage.  Call for your showing today!
